# Survival Analysis

# Load Library

```{r}
library(survival)
library(gtsummary)
library(survminer)
library(tidyverse)
library(broom)
library(lubridate)
library(haven)
library(dplyr)
library(corrplot)
library(mfp)
```

## Read Data

```{r}
stroke <- read_dta ("stroke_outcome.dta")
```

```{r}
summary(stroke)
```

```{r}
stroke <- stroke %>%
  mutate_if(is.labelled,~as_factor(.))
```

```{r}
summary(stroke)
```
